  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nCurrently it's only possible to set the header for one specific path:\r\n```properties\r\nquarkus.http.header.Pragma.value=no-cache\r\nquarkus.http.header.Pragma.path=/headers/pragma\r\nquarkus.http.header.Pragma.methods=GET,HEAD\r\n````\r\nIt would be nice to be able to do it for multiple paths. Something like:\r\n```properties\r\nquarkus.http.header.path.\"/static/*\".Cache-Control.value=max-age=31536000\r\nquarkus.http.header.path.\"/index.html\".Cache-Control.value=no-cache\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
